trans-unit.source:
If you do not define your own configuration for Google Consent Mode, the following settings are set automatically: <pre>

          window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
          function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}

          gtag('consent', 'default', {
          'ad_storage': 'denied',
          'ad_user_data': 'denied',
          'ad_personalization': 'denied',
          'analytics_storage': 'denied',
          'functionality_storage': 'denied',
          'personalization_storage': 'denied',
          'wait_for_update': 500
          });

          gtag('js', new Date());
          gtag('config', '<code class="tl_red">ID</code>');
          </pre>

          Please note that you have to enter this code yourself if you want to create your own configuration.
          The integration of the Google Tag Manager is done automatically via the following code:

          <pre>

          (function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
            new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
            j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
            'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
            })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','ID');
          </pre>

trans-unit.target:
Dacă nu definiți o configurație proprie pentru Google Consent Mode, următoarele setări vor fi aplicate automat: <pre>

          window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
          function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}

          gtag('consent', 'default', {
          'ad_storage': 'denied',
          'ad_user_data': 'denied',
          'ad_personalization': 'denied',
          'analytics_storage': 'denied',
          'functionality_storage': 'denied',
          'personalization_storage': 'denied',
          'wait_for_update': 500
          });

          gtag('js', new Date());
          gtag('config', '<code class="tl_red">ID</code>');
          </pre>

          Rețineți că trebuie să introduceți acest cod manual dacă doriți să creați o configurație proprie.
          Integrarea Google Tag Manager se realizează automat prin următorul cod:

          <pre>

          (function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
          new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
          j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
          'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
          })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','ID');
          </pre>
